data.description: Explore the charm of this meticulously remodeled 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home featuring a 2 car garage. Step inside to discover a seamless blend of modern upgrades throughout. The fenced backyard offers privacy and a perfect outdoor retreat. The downstairs 4th bedroom provides versatility, serving as either a private suite with an attached bathroom or an additional living space for entertaining. This property strikes the perfect balance between functionality and style, providing the ideal backdrop for comfortable living and hosting memorable gatherings. Welcome to your beautifully renovated home!
